OpenGL Circle
-------------

Sudo code to generate vertices to render a circle in opengl using GL_TRIANGLE_FAN
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	origin_x = 0
	origin_y = 0
	radius = 0.5
	segments = 10

	vertices = []

	vertices.push([origin_x, origin_y])

	for i = 0 to segments
		angle_rad = 2 * PI * (i/segments)
		x = origin_x + radius * cos(angle_rad)
		y = origin_y + radius * sin(angle_rad)
		vertices.push([x, y])

	vertices.push(vertices[1])